we say, "Make me something."

137
00:05:51,780 --> 00:05:54,900
And it goes off and it
writes a 1,000 lines of code

138
00:05:54,900 --> 00:05:57,000
and it says, "I made you something."

139
00:05:57,000 --> 00:05:59,790
And then it hands it to you
and hopefully it did it right.

140
00:05:59,790 --> 00:06:01,380
But more than likely what happened

141
00:06:01,380 --> 00:06:04,770
is that it got to a lot of
different decision points,

142
00:06:04,770 --> 00:06:08,070
a lot of details that you
left out of your prompt

143
00:06:08,070 --> 00:06:10,290
