186
00:07:39,210 --> 00:07:40,920
And then once we have those,

187
00:07:40,920 --> 00:07:43,140
then we bring the team
of developers in the room

188
00:07:43,140 --> 00:07:44,670
and we say, "Here's what you're building.

189
00:07:44,670 --> 00:07:45,990
Here's how you're building it.

190
00:07:45,990 --> 00:07:48,630
And here's all the different
tasks that you need to do."

191
00:07:48,630 --> 00:07:50,400
And we use those to go off

192
00:07:50,400 --> 00:07:52,530
and actually do the implementation.

193
00:07:52,530 --> 00:07:55,290
And that's how we solve for this problem

194
00:07:55,290 --> 00:07:56,610
